value.string: Easy care,, ground floor two bedroom unit with grassy area off lanai, and BBQ & pool off your front door. Very convenient. Granite counter tops. This Fannie Mae property can be purchased for as little as 3% down, with no PMI or appraisal, and is eligible for HomePath and HomePath Renovation mortgage financing. Being sold in "as is" condition. Seller will not pay for termite inspection nor HOA docs. Pets are allowed. Two tandum parking spaces. Act 142 prevails.

This apartment is located in the leasehold complex called Kanai A Nalu in the area known as Maalaea, near one of the harbors on Maui. #307 is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath unit and is tucked back in the 2nd building to help protect it from the elements, yet has a very nice ocean/mountain view overlooking the pool. Located on a sandy beach section and walking distance to the park at the end of the street. This Fannie Mae property is approved for HomePath Renovation financing, for as little as 3% down for owner occupants, with no appraisal or PMI. Go to HomePath.com for eligibility details. Seller will not pay for HOA docs nor termite inspection. Being sold in "as is" condition. Monthy LH payment is currently $803. In 2016 it changes to $964, then in 2026 it will be $1205. Lease renegotiates in 2036 & expires in 2066.

Located across the street from the ocean for a quick swim, this condo-hotel property has individual buildings with one unit up and one down. #116 is a ground floor unit, with the back lanai looking out on to the green space. Back bedroom is open with a large slider to close it off. Apt has tile floors, and a new hot water heater. Tenant occupied so need 48 hours notice. Unit can be purchased for as little as 3% down, and qualifies for HomePath Renovation financing. Go to HomePath.com for details. Eligibility restrictions may apply. No offers the first 3 days on MLS, then only Owner Occupants who will be living in the unit for the coming year can make an offer. Investors can make an offer after the 15th day on MLS. Being sold "as is". Seller will not pay for HOA docs nor termite inspection. Pets not allowed.

#216 is a direct oceanfront, 1 bedroom unit, with wonderful ocean and mtn views and is waiting for your decorative touches. On 2nd floor. Very high vaulted ceilings. Short term rentals allowed. This Fannie Mae property can be purchased as little as 3% down with no PMI or appraisal, and has been approved for HomePath and HomePath Renovation financing. Go to HomePath.com for details. Eligibility requirement apply so check with your lender. Being sold in "as is" condition. No offers the first 3 days on MLS, then ONLY owner occupants may make an offer, which means buyers will be living in the unit for the next 12 months. Investors may make an offer after the 15th day on HomePath/First Look. No company addendums. Small sandy beach to the right of the complex.

Nice, garden setting for this ground floor studio, near the pool in Napili Ridge. Currently this fee interest of this property is available with a separate 3rd party, although current amount needs to be verified and approved to purchase. Lease renegotiates in 2019. Tile throughout, with carpet in most of main living area. This Fannie Mae property has been approved for HomePath Renovation financing only. Go to HomePath.com for details. Eligibiity requirement apply. Being sold in "as is" condition. Seller will not pay for termite inspection. HOA and LH docs are negotiable. Parking stall #101. No company addendums.

Located at the end of the I building, this upper features a mirrored wall in the living room and the bedroom. Garden view off lanai. This Fannie Mae property is approved for HomePath and HomePath Renovation financing for as little as 3% down and no PMI. Eligibility requirements apply, so check with your favorite lender. Being sold in "as is" condition, with no seller's disclosure. Seller will not pay for termite inspection or HOA docs. Easy to show.

Easy access with this ground floor, 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath unit. This Fannie Mae property is approved for Homepath and HomePath Renovation financing for as little as 3% down, no PMI, and no appraisal. HomePath First Look has expired. Open to all offers. As per Hawaii State law, 48+ hours are needed to show. Listor must be present at showings. Seller will not pay for HOA documents, seller's disclosure, nor for a termite inspection. Property being sold in "as is" condition. Electric is not included in HOA, as per recent change. New HOA fee beginning 7/1/2013 to $585 with electric NOT included. Electric bill is given on first of month from office via the sub-meter reading, and due by the 20th of each month. Laundry room with a washer and dryer, is on the 3rd and 4th floor in building C.

Spacious, leasehold, 1 bedroom condo in this secure building located on the front row in the harbor area known as Maalaea. Code needed to enter building. This is a Fannie Mae HomePath property. No HomePath nor HomePath Renovation financing included. Being sold in "as is" condition. Small, peek-a-boo ocean view from the large lanai. A cat or small dog are allowed as well as bird(s) with Board approval. Nice BBQ and pool area on the ocean side of the complex. Laundry room around the corner from your front door. Easy to show.

Lovely, upgraded, upper unit that captures the fresh air, plus has a peaceful garden, plus Haleakala view from the front area. Freshly painted, new carpet in the bedrooms, ceramic tile in kitchen and bathrooms, granite counter tops in the kitchen and bathroom vanities, newer cabinets, stainless steel refrigerator are all but a few of the upgrades this owner occupant has done. Definitely pride of ownership shows in this 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath unit. Parking in front of the unit. Easy to show with 24 hours notice. Pets allowed. In January, 2014 the HOA fee will go down to $344.16. A beautifully maintained unit that is easy to show.

Private, well maintained, 2nd floor, one bedroom unit in D-building that overlooks the garden/gulch area. The leasehold interest has been offered to be purchased in the past, but if available at this time & cost involved, Buyer needs to do their own due diligence. Unit is tiled and kitchen was upgraded some time in the past. This is a Fannie Mae HomePath property and is approved for HomePath Renovation Mortgage Financing. See your favorite HomePath lender for details. Eligibility requirements may apply. Fannie Mae will not pay for termite inspection or HOA documents. No offers the first 3 days on MLS. Then only buyers who will be owner occupants may make an offer in the first 15 days in MLS. An Owner Occupant Certificate available on www.HomePath.com. As per HomePath/First Look, all buyers may make an offer from the 16th day on MLS on.

This ground floor, Fannie Mae property features the desirable 2 bedroom, 2 bath model in the complex called Kihei Villages. Unit is all tiled for easy care. Large, enclosed back yard which appears to be almost all concrete and very private. One pet is allowed. No offers the first 3 days and then only Owner Occupants may make an offer for the first 20 days. After the 20th day, all buyers may make an offer. An Owner Occupant Certificate will need to be included with offer, if applicable. Parking stall is 334. Seller will not pay for HOA docs or a termite inspection. Easy to show.

Looking for a home with the convenience of a condo? This second floor apartment is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath in Napili Villa. Two parking stalls - 335 and 336. The open floor plan for the living room, dining area and kitchen makes for an easy flow. The vaulted ceiling adds another touch of airiness. Lanai right off dining area has a large storage area. When the breeze blows the palm away, you even have a peek-a-boo ocean view. No offers the first 3 days on HomePath.com/First Look, and then only Owner Occupants may make an offer for the first 20 days. After that, all buyers may make an offer. Seller will not pay HOA docs or a termite inspection. Being sold in "as is" condition. For the unit, put #22-8, which is for building 22, unit 8.

This Fannie Mae property is located on the ground floor of the C building, away from the highway. Lanai is on the back side of the living room for your outdoor living. Complex has a pool, BBQ area and workout room. No company addendums accepted. Being sold in "as is" condition. Seller will not pay for the HOA docs nor a termite inspection. As per state law, no Seller's Disclosure given. No offers the first 3 days, then only Owner Occupants may make an offer. After the 20th day on MLS, then all buyers may make an offer. Parking stall is #57. Unit is easy to show.

This Fannie Mae property is located on the 2nd floor of the E-building. Lanai is on the back side with the living room for your outdoor living. Peek-a-boo ocean view to the left as you look out. Floors are tiled and bedroom has carpet. Complex has a pool, BBQ area and a workout room. No company addendums accepted. Being sold in "as is" condition. Seller will not pay for the HOA documents nor a termite inspection. As per state law, no Seller's Disclosure given. No offers the first 3 days, and then only Owner Occupants may make an offer. After the 20th day on MLS then all buyers may make an offer. Parking stall is 228. Unit is easy to show.

Superb location, views and condition! This three bedroom Hokulani Golf Villa is located at the top of this sought after community on the 18th hole of Elleair Golf Course. There are outstanding views down the fairway on out to the Pacific Ocean. The home is in mint condition and has barely been used. Many upgrades include African Mahogany cabinetry, travertine in the master bath, granite counters, pull out drawers, a large capacity refrigerator and wine cooler. This particular residence is better than new because it has custom electric shades and window coverings. It’s floor plan has 12 ft. ceilings in the great room, the master bedroom on the ground floor and a versatile den/office. The second floor includes two spacious guest bedrooms, one with a private deck and a family room/entertainment area between them.

This Fannie Mae HomePath property is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath apartment and is a walk-down, literally, to the ground floor which makes it a cooler place to live. Complex has a pool and BBQ area. The Seller will not pay for HOA docs or a termite inspection. As per state law, no Seller's Disclosure will be given. Parking stall is #61. Being sold in "as is" condition. Easy to show.

A-211 is located in one of the "front" buildings which give you easy access to the beach, a very nice ocean and outer island views, yet is still steps to one of the two pools. The tennis courts are at the back of the property. This bank owner property is a 2 bedroom, 2 bath and located on the 2nd floor of the A-building. Being sold is in "as is" condition. The carpet is in good shape. Parking stall is #33. There is a Special Assessment to all owners of $798 for replacement of the lanai flower boxes and will be due over the next two years. Also, each upstairs unit will be assessed approximately $2500-3000 for new railings over the next 2 years. Easy to show - on lockbox.

This well appointed and remodeled condo is ready to move into or vacation rent. The unit has been well maintained and upgrades include granite counters, new carpeting, and a recently renovated Master bath. Maui Kamaole is a favorite destination and popular rental in sought after South Kihei. You are minutes to fabulous dining, white sand beaches, golf and shopping. The pools and landscaping are first rate, just like the condition of this 2 bedroom, two bath unit. Easy to show!

Rare, fee simple 2 bedroom, 1 bath, lovely, well maintained apartment and complex, with a pool for only $335,000. Front of unit is a large living room, kitchen and dining area. In the back are the 2 bedrooms with bath in the center. Across the street from the park, ocean, and easy walking distance to shopping and restaurants. Because this is located in the B-building, it is much quieter being away from the road. Pergo-style laminate floors for easy care, remodeled kitchen with a brand new dishwasher and bathroom makes this a turn key unit. Just add your furniture and you are ready to make this your home. An additional parking stall is now being rented, so please park in one of the 2 assigned spaces at the showings. Tenant occupied so we need at least 24 hours notice for only qualified buyers. Pool has an entertainment area next to it, plus there is a laundry room, BBQ area, and even a separate place to put bicycles.

This Fannie Mae, ocean front property has a fantastic ocean view. Miles and miles of sandy beach that stretches out in both directions to enjoy the great outdoor life here on Maui. Swimming, snorkeling and even windsurfing are right out in front. This leasehold, one bedroom unit has a newer kitchen and vanity cabinets with ceramic tile floors, and large mirrors that bring the view into the unit. It is just waiting for your furnishing touches. Parking is covered, on ground floor. Easy to show.
